Author: yugogrl2000
Text: That is exactly the kind of thing that I was talking about! I do this from time to time and forget it is not a normal thing to say.

Author: throwaway71871127198
Text: At my work the other week they were going to host a speed-eating competition. Someone suggested I should sign up as my team’s competitor and without thinking I said “oh God no way, I hate eating in front of other people, I’d die” like I completely forgot that that’s a weird thing to say to normal people haha
